<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8"/>
  <title>[VOUCHERS] Mise à jour — {{repo_full_name}}</title>
  <style>
    body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background:#f9f6ee; margin:0; padding:0; }
    .container { max-width:680px; margin:32px auto; background:#fff; border-radius:8px; box-shadow:0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,.1); overflow:hidden; }
    .header { background:#2e7d32; color:#fff; padding:24px 32px; }
    .header h1 { margin:0; font-size:20px; }
    .badge { display:inline-block; background:#c8e6c9; color:#1b5e20; border-radius:4px; padding:2px 8px; font-size:12px; font-weight:600; }
    .body { padding:24px 32px; }
    .meta { font-size:13px; color:#555; margin-bottom:16px; }
    .commit-list { border-left:3px solid #2e7d32; padding-left:16px; margin:16px 0; }
    .commit-item { margin-bottom:10px; }
    .commit-sha { font-family:monospace; font-size:12px; color:#2e7d32; }
    .commit-msg { font-size:14px; color:#222; }
    .btn { background:#2e7d32; color:#fff; padding:10px 28px; border-radius:4px; text-decoration:none; font-size:14px; display:inline-block; margin-top:16px; }
    .footer { background:#f5f5f5; padding:14px 32px; font-size:12px; color:#999; border-top:1px solid #eee; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="container">
  <div class="header">
    <h1>🌾 Mise à jour Vouchers Agriculture</h1>
    <p style="margin:4px 0 0;font-size:13px;opacity:.8">Plateforme de subventions agricoles · FASO DIGITALISATION</p>
  </div>
  <div class="body">
    <div class="meta">
      <strong>Dépôt :</strong> <a href="{{repo_url}}" style="color:#2e7d32">{{repo_full_name}}</a> &nbsp;|&nbsp;
      <strong>Branche :</strong> <span class="badge">{{branch}}</span> &nbsp;|&nbsp;
      <strong>{{commit_count}} commit(s)</strong> &nbsp;|&nbsp;
      <strong>Auteur :</strong> {{author_login}}
    </div>
    <p style="color:#555;font-size:14px;">
      Une mise à jour a été poussée sur la plateforme des vouchers agricoles.
      Veuillez vérifier les changements ci-dessous et valider leur impact métier.
    </p>
    <div class="commit-list">
      {{#each commits}}
      <div class="commit-item">
        <span class="commit-sha">{{shortSha this.id}}</span>
        <span class="commit-msg"> — {{truncate this.message len=100}}</span>
        <div style="font-size:12px;color:#888;">{{this.author.name}}</div>
      </div>
      {{/each}}
    </div>
    <a href="{{compare_url}}" class="btn">Consulter les modifications</a>
  </div>
  <div class="footer">FASO DIGITALISATION — notifier-ms · {{rendered_at}}</div>
</div>
</body>
</html>
